Defining URLhttp://terminology.hl7.org/NamingSystem/ISO3166Part3
NameISO3166Part3
Statusactive
Definition

ISO 3166-3 establishes a code that represents non-current country names, i.e. the country names deleted from ISO 3166 since its first publication in 1974.

PublisherInternational Organization for Standardization (ISO)

Identifiers

TypeValuePreferred
URIurn:iso:std:iso:3166:-3true
